    Wix Pricing Exploration User Story

    As a potential Wix user, I compare different pricing plans and features, so that I can choose the best plan that fits my needs.

    Success definition: Given I am on the Wix homepage after exploring from Jamiphy When I navigate through the Wix pricing information and plan comparison sections Then I should see a variety of premium plans listed with their prices, features, and a clear 14-day money-back guarantee.
